"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-28-team-gb-star-adam-peaty-consoled-bbc-reporter-olympics-agony-21314825\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Team GB starAdam Peatywas consoled by aBBCreporter after missing out on yet anotherOlympicgold medal by just 0.02 seconds.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 122, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After a fairly slow start to the 100m breaststroke final in Paris, Peaty powered into contention in the final 50 meters as he sensed athird consecutive Olympic gold medal.\", \"from\": 124, \"to\": 295, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 184, \"end\": 189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999991655386, \"rank\": 8.345284007607208e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That would have seen Peaty, 29, become only the second man after American legend Michael Phelps to win the same swimming event at three successive Olympics.\", \"from\": 297, \"to\": 453, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 362, \"end\": 370, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999437310190853, \"rank\": 4.682589188689524e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 378, \"end\": 392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7490060866866793e-47, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A competitive and thrilling final all came down to the final stroke, with Italy's Nicolo Martinenghi finishing just 0.02 seconds ahead of joint-silver medallists Peaty and American Nic Fink to clinch a shock gold.\", \"from\": 455, \"to\": 668, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 529, \"end\": 534, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.998680225178391, \"rank\": 0.0012290001957312485, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 537, \"end\": 555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicol\\u00f2_Martinenghi\", \"score\": 0.9999999871765796, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nicolo Martinenghi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicol\\u00f2_Martinenghi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicol\\u00f2_Martinenghi\"}, {\"begin\": 627, \"end\": 635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999437310190853, \"rank\": 4.682589188689524e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 636, \"end\": 644, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nic_Fink\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nic Fink\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nic_Fink\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nic_Fink\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While Peaty was unable to make more history in the pool and take home a third gold medal, he did secure a sixth Olympic medal after returning to the sport following a break due to mental health issues and alcoholism.\", \"from\": 670, \"to\": 886, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Peaty initially appeared in good spirits in an interview withBBC Sportstraight after the final but began to choke up as he reflected on his emotional and inspiring journey.\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 1060, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TheParis 2024 silver medallistsaid: 'It has been a very long way back.\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1132, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I look at the score there and you would never think in your wildest dreams that it would be 59 seconds to win it.\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1246, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In my heart I have already won\\\" \\u00e2\\u009d\\u00a4\\u00ef\\u00b8\\u008fAdam Peaty let all his emotions out after he won silver in the men's breaststroke final \\u00f0\\u009f\\u0098\\u00a5We are very proud of you Adam!#BBCOlympics#Olympics#Paris2024pic.twitter.com/JxUFvunn2Z  'I gave it my absolute all.\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1495, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I executed it as well as I could.\", \"from\": 1496, \"to\": 1529, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not about the end goal, it's about the process.\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1582, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It does not matter what time it says on the scoreboard, I think in my heart I have already won.\", \"from\": 1583, \"to\": 1678, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am so happy that I can race against the best in the world and still come joint-second.\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1769, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In my heart I have won, these are happy tears.\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1816, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I gave my absolute best every single day and I cannot be upset about that.\", \"from\": 1818, \"to\": 1893, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am almost an older man here now.\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1928, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I can not have that relentless pursuit every single day without a sacrifice of some sort - they come in every single form.\", \"from\": 1930, \"to\": 2053, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's very hard to compete with the younger ones, so I am very happy with that.'\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2133, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Peaty continued to look emotional as he hugged his wife and young child in the stands after coming so close to another Olympic gold.\", \"from\": 2135, \"to\": 2267, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Analysing Peaty's performance in the final, former freestyle world swimming champion Mark Foster said on BBC One: 'Adam mentioned that he was one or two percent off - that is the difference between winning and losing.\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2486, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2354, \"end\": 2365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Foster_the_People\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.220163807065789e-30, \"text\": \"Mark Foster\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Foster_the_People\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Foster_the_People\"}, {\"begin\": 2374, \"end\": 2381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_One\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.984750881721736e-20, \"text\": \"BBC One\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_One\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_One\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An incredible journey back to the podium.Proud of you, Adam.#Paris2024pic.twitter.com/QU5tw5m2fa  'You could pick it to pieces and think: \\\"He could've done this, he could've done that on the evening\\\" - and we could pick everyone else to pieces - but it is about who manages their emotions best and gets the best result.\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2807, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'But that was his best result for tonight.'\", \"from\": 2809, \"to\": 2852, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Double Olympic champion Rebecca Adlington added: 'You could see Adam was genuinely happy.\", \"from\": 2854, \"to\": 2943, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2878, \"end\": 2895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca_Adlington\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rebecca Adlington\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca_Adlington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca_Adlington\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You could see they were happy tears.\", \"from\": 2944, \"to\": 2980, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am just emotional for him because, as an athlete, you know what he has been through.\", \"from\": 2982, \"to\": 3069, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have achieved nothing compared to Adam - what he has achieved is unbelievable - I can not even get my head around it.\", \"from\": 3070, \"to\": 3189, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'He is such a role model for the rest of that team - people look up to him and he just has so much respect.\", \"from\": 3191, \"to\": 3298, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is amazing to see him smile.'\", \"from\": 3299, \"to\": 3331, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GB remain without a gold medal at the Paris Olympics but Peaty's silver takes them to four overall - two silvers and two bronze after two days of action in the French capital.\", \"from\": 3333, \"to\": 3513, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3333, \"end\": 3340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999999999968168, \"rank\": 3.3779600289575005e-12, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 3498, \"end\": 3504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8610448445132834, \"rank\": 0.14431974673313705, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 3515, \"to\": 3563, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 3565, \"to\": 3635, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:BBC presenter Clare Balding criticises Engla